  "detailed_description": "Edessa: School of Wizardry is a dark themed action game set in a magical universe. Fight the demons that have plagued the world and cast your spells with the Edessa's unique spellcasting mechanic. Fight the bosses, solve the puzzles and come out on top.<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/9941c8d3cf984c9ff548d708b8cf3ed8.poster.avif?t=1659026739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/9941c8d3cf984c9ff548d708b8cf3ed8.webm?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/9941c8d3cf984c9ff548d708b8cf3ed8.mp4?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>In this world, it takes more than just pushing a button to cast a spell. To perform your desired spell, you need to draw the required symbols. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/83f27a6daf68883f3b0923af20fed338.poster.avif?t=1659026739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/83f27a6daf68883f3b0923af20fed338.webm?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/83f27a6daf68883f3b0923af20fed338.mp4?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Find your way through the house by solving the puzzles.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/29aeac03aae8f54742411565734851b6.poster.avif?t=1659026739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/29aeac03aae8f54742411565734851b6.webm?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/29aeac03aae8f54742411565734851b6.mp4?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Explore the Gobeklitepe. The oldest temple in the world.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "Edessa: School of Wizardry is a dark themed action game set in a magical universe. Fight the demons that have plagued the world and cast your spells with the Edessa's unique spellcasting mechanic. Fight the bosses, solve the puzzles and come out on top.<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/9941c8d3cf984c9ff548d708b8cf3ed8.poster.avif?t=1659026739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/9941c8d3cf984c9ff548d708b8cf3ed8.webm?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/9941c8d3cf984c9ff548d708b8cf3ed8.mp4?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>In this world, it takes more than just pushing a button to cast a spell. To perform your desired spell, you need to draw the required symbols. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/83f27a6daf68883f3b0923af20fed338.poster.avif?t=1659026739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/83f27a6daf68883f3b0923af20fed338.webm?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/83f27a6daf68883f3b0923af20fed338.mp4?t=1659026739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Find your way through the house by solving the puzzles.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823670/extras/29aeac03aae8f5